
To build:
$ docker build . -t micropython

To run:
$ docker run -it --device=/dev/ttyUSB0 micropython /bin/bash

To connect to serial:
$ screen /dev/ttlUSB0 115200

Was able to successfully execute the 'make flash' described here:
https://esp-idf.readthedocs.io/en/latest/get-started/index.html#start-a-project

Left off here: https://github.com/micropython/micropython/tree/master/ports/esp32#building-the-firmware
